{"tw": {"2421360": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "在赛博世界和100个道侣修仙", "steam_appid": 2421360, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<h1>重要提示</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你想要的充滿魅力和趣味的浪漫互動</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在建立角色介面/選擇角色介面（選擇存檔/變更難度介面）同時按 ：S+F</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421360/extras/b99fcb6a2f57401a9f965a3c01df6dc3.avif?t=1774580980\" width=1170 height=273 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421360/extras/9ed13fe797dfa0cee632346cccb10b75.avif?t=1774580980\" width=1170 height=273 /></span></p></p><br><h1>關於此遊戲</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你穿越到一個陌生的遊戲小世界中，這個世界是一個科技修仙的世界</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但是你想以其他方式飛升：讓所有女性都成為自己的道情侶。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與所有道情侶雙修升級：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所有道情侶都可以雙修升級，無需打怪。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421360/extras/8c53d191266fcbfdf157fb92aea96faf.poster.avif?t=1774580980\" width=260 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421360/extras/8c53d191266fcbfdf157fb92aea96faf.webm?t=1774580980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421360/extras/8c53d191266fcbfdf157fb92aea96faf.mp4?t=1774580980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421360/extras/7bb2b25319d7b11417361717f4ce868e.poster.avif?t=1774580980\" width=260 height=160 ><source src