80980\" width=780 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421360/extras/684a79fd669b80c93a0c3a764e683eb6.webm?t=1774580980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421360/extras/684a79fd669b80c93a0c3a764e683eb6.mp4?t=1774580980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲特色</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小型大世界：隨機女角色，每個都不同。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全部可攻略：所有女角色，都可以攻略。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不同場所超多動作：多個場所多個地點可進行運動</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多種金手指：多種職業可供選擇，每個職業都有一個金手指。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隨機初始天賦：初始天賦可進行隨機，各種強力天賦幫助自由暢玩。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >養成玩法：裝備威能，裝備強化，裝備洗練，裝備熔鑄，養成玩法該有的都有了。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >重複挑戰：隨機肉鴿刷寶玩法，刷寶不再單調。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >道情侶特殊體質：透過雙修可以為道情侶增加特殊體質，幫助遊戲養成。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >夜店消費玩法：透過消費可以去夜店唱歌，想和誰唱都可以。</p></li></ul>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你穿越到一個陌生的遊戲小世界中，這個世界是一個科技修仙的世界</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但是你想以其他方式飛升：讓所有女性都成為自己的道情侶。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與所有道情侶雙修升級：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所有道情侶都可以雙修升級，無需打怪。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421360/extras/8c53d191266fcbfdf157fb92aea96faf.poster.avif?t=1774580980\" width=260 height=160 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421360/extras/8c53d191266fcbfdf157fb92aea96faf.webm?t=1774580980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421360/extras/8c53d191266fcbfdf157fb92aea96faf.mp4?t=1774580980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"b