screen (save selection).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421360/extras/536df3487211e475ecac5a47be1329d6.avif?t=1774580980\" width=1170 height=273 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421360/extras/1d69f92b1a9f66db7d3c9350af97b2a5.avif?t=1774580980\" width=1170 height=273 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You've been transported to a strange little game world, a world of technological cultivation and immortality, but you aspire to ascend in a different way: by making all women your Daoist partners.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level up through dual cultivation with all your Daoist partners:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All Daoist partners can level up through dual cultivation without having to fight monsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Basic Gameplay</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use skills to fight monsters and level up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421360/extras/3ea8e634c8036b80483be10a7b7ad580.poster.avif?t=1774580980\" width=780 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421360/extras/3ea8e634c8036b80483be10a7b7ad580.webm?t=1774580980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421360/extras/3ea8e634c8036b80483be10a7b7ad580.mp4?t=1774580980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Conduct breakthrough battles, dodge tribulations, and break through shackles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421360/extras/684a79fd669b80c93a0c3a764e683eb6.poster.avif?t=1774580980\" width=780 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421360/extras/684a79fd669b80c93a0c3a764e683eb6.webm?t=1774580980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421360/extras/684a79fd669b80c93a0c3a764e683eb6.mp4?t=1774580980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game Features</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Small but Vast World: Randomly selected female characters, each unique.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All Romantic: All female characters are romanceable.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple Actions in Different Locations: Multiple locations and activities available.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple Cheat Codes: Choose from multiple classes, each with a unique cheat code.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Random Initial Talents: Initial talents are randomized, with various powerful talents aiding in free gameplay.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Development System: Equipment power enhancement, equipment strengthening, equipment refinement, equipment forging—all the essential development gameplay is included.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Repetitive Challenges: Random roguelike treasure hunting gameplay, making treasure hunting less monotonous.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Daoist Partner Special Constitutions: Through dual cultivation, you can grant your Daoist partner special constitutions, aiding in game development.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nightclub spending: You can spend money to go to nightclubs to sing, sing with whomever you want, and if you get excited.</p></li></ul>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You've been transported to a strange little game world, a world of technological cultivation and immortality, but you aspire to ascend in a different way: by making all women your Daoist partners.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level up through dual cultivation with all your Daoist partners:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All Daoist partners can level up through dual cultivation without having to fight monsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Basic Gameplay</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use skills to fight monsters and level up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421360/extras/3ea8e634c8036b80483be10a7b7ad580.poster.avif?t=1774580980\" width=780 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421360/extras/3ea8e634c8036b80483be10a7b7ad580.webm?t=1774580980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421360/extras/3ea8e634c8036b80483be10a7b7ad580.mp4?t=1774580980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Conduct breakthrough battles, dodge tribulations, and break through shackles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421360/extras/684a79fd669b80c93a0c3a764e683eb6.poster.avif?t=1774580980\" width=780 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421360/extras/684a79fd669b80c93a0c3a764e683eb6.webm?t=1774580980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2421360/extras/684a79fd669b80c93a0c3